summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property and property rights and privileges in Snohomish County for transmission system right of way, as provided for by Ordinance No. 43547, as amended by Ordinance No. 44097, being Cause No. 20600 in the Superior Court of Snohomish County, Washington, in so far as the same affects certain of the property therein described; and appropriating money to pay all taxable costs incurred by the parties to said condemnation suit whose property is dismissed by this ordinance.
